                    <bibl><ptr target="#GVCyr"/> <citedRange>043</citedRange></bibl>. 
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#gl-jmr1983"/>, n. <citedRange>32.d</citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>33.1468</citedRange></bibl>.
